# Integration test JARs

This directory holds cloud-specific Chronon assembly JARs used by the integration tests.
The JARs are excluded from version control (see .gitignore) because they are ~200 MB each.

## Required JARs

| File             | Cloud target |
|------------------|--------------|
| cloud_aws.jar    | AWS          |
| cloud_azure.jar  | Azure        |
| cloud_gcp.jar    | GCP          |
| cloud_k8s.jar    | Kubernetes   |

## How to build / obtain them

Build from the Chronon repo with the assembly target for the relevant cloud profile, e.g.:

```bash
# from the root of the chronon repo
sbt "project spark_uber_jar" "set assembly / assemblyJarName := \"cloud_gcp.jar\"" assembly
# repeat with the appropriate profile/settings for aws, azure, k8s
```

Copy or symlink the resulting JARs into this directory before running the integration tests.

The integration tests skip automatically when the required JAR is absent — they are not
expected to run in CI unless the JARs are explicitly provided.
